        <span class="keyword-btn pending" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: #2A2723; color: #8A8478; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 0.95rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; border: 1px solid rgba(232,226,213,0.15); cursor: not-allowed;">#pontianak vs la llorona similarities</span>
