            <h4 style="color: var(--accent-dark, #7A1212); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive;">Q: Universal themes?</h4>
            <p style="color: #2A2723; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>A:</strong> Vengeance, loss, betrayal</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" style="background: #E8E2D5; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent, #B91C1C); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transition: transform 0.2s ease;">
